{"id": "13394", "revid": "31124876", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=13394", "title": "Derelict Home (Slums District)", "text": "Derelict Home is an empty house in &lt;a href=\"Athkatla\"&gt;Athkatla's&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Slums%20District\"&gt;Slums&lt;/a&gt; during \"\".\nIt remains empty of inhabitants, unless and until &lt;a href=\"Jaheira\"&gt;Jaheira&lt;/a&gt; is cursed by three mages hired by &lt;a href=\"Baron%20Ployer\"&gt;Baron Ployer&lt;/a&gt; in the &lt;a href=\"Sea%27s%20Bounty%20Tavern\"&gt;Sea's Bounty Tavern&lt;/a&gt; at the &lt;a href=\"Athkatla%20Docks\"&gt;Athkatla Docks&lt;/a&gt;, thus beginning one of Jaheira's &lt;a href=\"Companions\"&gt;Companion&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"quests\"&gt;quests&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Save%20Jaheira%20from%20Baron%20Ployer%27s%20Curse\"&gt;Save Jaheira from Baron Ployer's Curse&lt;/a&gt;\nDepending upon which choices are made after the curse is given, one or more of the mages, &lt;a href=\"Terrece\"&gt;Terrece&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Gracien\"&gt;Gracien&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Malacazar\"&gt;Malacazar&lt;/a&gt;, can be found here along with Ployer, at the conclusion of the quest.\nContainers.\nThere are two containers in the home, neither of which are trapped or locked."}
