{"id": "49976", "revid": "44830706", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=49976", "title": "Lemzenn", "text": "The Dark Moon Monk Lemzenn is a character from and part of &lt;a href=\"Rasaad%27s%20Journey\"&gt;Rasaad's Journey&lt;/a&gt; questline. He can be found in the &lt;a href=\"Heretic%20Temple\"&gt;Heretic Temple&lt;/a&gt; general area.\nGameplay.\nHe is lurking in tall grasses amidst the tree canopy shadows, northeast of the &lt;a href=\"Bound%20Sun%20Soul%20Monk\"&gt;Bound Sun Soul Monk&lt;/a&gt; group. You can confront him, and through various dialogue choices to learn what he is doing. You could end up turning him hostile as well. \nLemzenn has all the abilities, immunities and special bonuses afforded to a Dark Moon Monk, and commensurate with his 10th Level experience. He'll use those if he needs to defend himself.\nMod content.\nThe &lt;a href=\"Sword%20Coast%20Stratagems\"&gt;Sword Coast Stratagems&lt;/a&gt; mod provides a new AI monk script. Three potions are provided to him and scripted for use to heal or boost abilities."}
