{"id": "50847", "revid": "31124876", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=50847", "title": "Small Spider (Bloated)", "text": "This Small Spider will only appear after a &lt;a href=\"Bloated%20Spider\"&gt;Bloated Spider&lt;/a&gt; has been killed. A total of five of them will immediately be released upon the bloated spider's death. They are permanently hasted, moving as fast as a character wearing &lt;a href=\"The%20Paws%20of%20the%20Cheetah\"&gt;The Paws of the Cheetah&lt;/a&gt;. This provides them with the ability to swarm a single party member and with their 4 attacks per round, inflict some pretty rapid damage in a short amount of time. However, like other &lt;a href=\"Small%20Spider\"&gt;Small Spider&lt;/a&gt;s, they don't possess the ability to inflict a &lt;a href=\"Poison\"&gt;Poison&lt;/a&gt; status effect upon a successful hit, a feature of their &lt;a href=\"Mutated%20Spider\"&gt;Mutated Spider&lt;/a&gt; cousins.\nCompared to a typical small spider, a few of their stats have been altered to make them slightly more difficult to hit successfully. This includes a reduction in &lt;a href=\"armor%20class\"&gt;armor class&lt;/a&gt; from 4 to 1 and &lt;a href=\"THAC0\"&gt;THAC0&lt;/a&gt; from 16 to 10. On the flip side however, their &lt;a href=\"hit%20point\"&gt;hit point&lt;/a&gt;s have been reduced from 32 to 8 and &lt;a href=\"XP\"&gt;XP&lt;/a&gt; from 300 to 100."}
