{"id": "4310", "revid": "31124876", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=4310", "title": "Southeast Baldur's Gate", "text": "Southeast Baldur's Gate is one of nine districts of &lt;a href=\"Baldur%27s%20Gate%20%28city%29\"&gt;Baldur's Gate city&lt;/a&gt; and is one of the poor areas south of the inner wall. The points of interest are the &lt;a href=\"Blade%20and%20Stars\"&gt;Blade and Stars&lt;/a&gt; inn, the shops and an unnamed inn near the wall.\nInside the Blade and Stars.\nGround floor\nSecond floor\nThird floor\nOthers.\n&lt;a href=\"Gantolandan%27s%20Home\"&gt;Gantolandan's Home&lt;/a&gt; is part of &lt;a href=\"Narlen%20Darkwalk\"&gt;Narlen Darkwalk&lt;/a&gt;'s tests for the &lt;a href=\"Thieves%27%20Guild\"&gt;Thieves' Guild&lt;/a&gt;. Imitate a cat when &lt;a href=\"Gantolandan\"&gt;Gantolandan&lt;/a&gt; queries, half asleep, \"who goes there\". He does not have a cat, though. Questioned again, say you are a stray cat.\nThere is a &lt;a href=\"Warehouses%20%28southeast%20Baldur%27s%20Gate%29%23AR1303\"&gt;warehouse&lt;/a&gt; at &lt;a href=\"Coordinates\"&gt;850.1960&lt;/a&gt; and inside &lt;a href=\"Nadarin\"&gt;Nadarin&lt;/a&gt; will give you the quest &lt;a href=\"Basilisk%20on%20the%20Loose\"&gt;Basilisk on the loose&lt;/a&gt;.\nYou can catch two robbers named &lt;a href=\"Taxek\"&gt;Taxek&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Michael\"&gt;Michael&lt;/a&gt; robbing a &lt;a href=\"Generic%20homes%20%28southeast%20Baldur%27s%20Gate%29%23AR1316\"&gt;house&lt;/a&gt; for some decent loot and a modest amount of XP.\nAt &lt;a href=\"Coordinates\"&gt;1700.2300&lt;/a&gt; there is an &lt;a href=\"Generic%20Tavern%20and%20Inn%20%28Baldur%27s%20Gate%29%23AR1306\"&gt;Inn and Tavern&lt;/a&gt; where you will find &lt;a href=\"Euric\"&gt;Euric&lt;/a&gt; (see the quest &lt;a href=\"Nadine%20and%20Euric\"&gt;Nadine and Euric&lt;/a&gt;) on the first floor. On the second floor you can talk to &lt;a href=\"Sanadal%20Gwist\"&gt;Sanadal Gwist&lt;/a&gt; and deliver some unfortunate news that she takes surprisingly well.\nReputation Trap.\nIf your Reputation is lower than 3 you will be attacked by a group of three &lt;a href=\"Flaming%20Fist%20Enforcer%20%28Baldur%27s%20Gate%29%23FLAMPUN\"&gt;Flaming Fist Enforcers&lt;/a&gt;, a &lt;a href=\"Flaming%20Fist%20Scout\"&gt;Flaming Fist Scout&lt;/a&gt; and a &lt;a href=\"Flaming%20Fist%20Battle%20Wizard\"&gt;Flaming Fist Battle Wizard&lt;/a&gt;. This group of soldiers will attack suddenly both on the streets and in the &lt;a href=\"Blade%20and%20Stars\"&gt;Blade and Stars&lt;/a&gt;.\nTransitions.\nCity map overview.\n City grid you are at the X:\n o|o|o &lt;a href=\"Northwest%20Baldur%27s%20Gate\"&gt;NW&lt;/a&gt;|&lt;a href=\"North%20Baldur%27s%20Gate\"&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;|&lt;a href=\"Northeast%20Baldur%27s%20Gate\"&gt;NE&lt;/a&gt; \n o|o|o &lt;a href=\"West%20Baldur%27s%20Gate\"&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;|&lt;a href=\"Central%20Baldur%27s%20Gate\"&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;|&lt;a href=\"East%20Baldur%27s%20Gate\"&gt;E&lt;/a&gt; \n o|o|X &lt;a href=\"Southwest%20Baldur%27s%20Gate\"&gt;SW&lt;/a&gt;|&lt;a href=\"South%20Baldur%27s%20Gate\"&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;|SE"}
