{"id": "2760", "revid": "47673695", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=2760", "title": "Spear", "text": "Spears are very basic 2-handed weapons with a range of 2\u00a0ft. Wielders of this weapon can hide behind a tank and still be able to attack the enemy. It can inflict 1d6 points of piercing damage and it has a speed factor of 6. The weapon weighs 5\u00a0lbs and it requires at least 5 &lt;a href=\"Strength\"&gt;Strength&lt;/a&gt; to wield it. &lt;a href=\"Barbarian\"&gt;Barbarian&lt;/a&gt;s, &lt;a href=\"fighter\"&gt;fighter&lt;/a&gt;s, &lt;a href=\"paladin\"&gt;paladin&lt;/a&gt;s, &lt;a href=\"ranger\"&gt;ranger&lt;/a&gt;s, &lt;a href=\"bard\"&gt;bard&lt;/a&gt;s, &lt;a href=\"druid\"&gt;druid&lt;/a&gt;s and &lt;a href=\"Shaman\"&gt;shamans&lt;/a&gt; can wield this kind of weapon. This item appears in all the where it can be bought in most weapon stores. Spears are also the standard weapon for &lt;a href=\"Tasloi\"&gt;Tasloi&lt;/a&gt;s."}
