a&gt; one &lt;a href=\"animal\"&gt;animal&lt;/a&gt; at a distance of up to 40\u202fft can be &lt;a href=\"charmed\"&gt;charmed&lt;/a&gt; with a power of 0 and will protect the druid and their allies from enemies for a duration of 1\u202fhour or until &lt;a href=\"Dispel%20Magic\"&gt;dispelled&lt;/a&gt;. A save vs. spell at a penalty of 4 is allowed against this ability from the &lt;a href=\"Specialist%20Mage\"&gt;school of enchantment&lt;/a&gt;, and the charm may be negated by the target's &lt;a href=\"magic%20resistance\"&gt;magic resistance&lt;/a&gt;. See also the &lt;a href=\"%23Notes\"&gt;notes&lt;/a&gt;.\nUp to another 6 times,&lt;a href=\"%23charges\"&gt;&lt;/a&gt; a &lt;a href=\"Shambling%20Mound%20%28Staff%20of%20the%20Woodlands%29\"&gt;shambling mound&lt;/a&gt; can be called and will appear at a desired location within a range of 40\u202fft, to aid the summoner for a duration of 100\u202fsec."}
