{"id": "8343", "revid": "8506165", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=8343", "title": "Stonefire", "text": "Stonefire is an enchanted battle axe +3 which inflicts 1d8 +3 slashing damage and +2 points of fire damage. It has THAC0\u00a0bonus of -3, a speed factor 4 and it weighs 7 lbs. This item appears in and .\nLocation.\nSold exclusively by &lt;a href=\"Bernard\"&gt;Bernard&lt;/a&gt; in his improved store. \nDescription.\nThere is no known reference in the Forgotten Realms to this item or the dwarven lineage mentioned in the description. However, the material stonefire is well-known amongst Drow craftsmen for its explosive properties."}
