{"id": "13544", "revid": "52556189", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=13544", "title": "Storehouse (Bridge District)", "text": "This Storehouse is a nondescript generic building located in &lt;a href=\"Athkatla\"&gt;Athkatla&lt;/a&gt;'s &lt;a href=\"Bridge%20District\"&gt;Bridge District&lt;/a&gt;. It is next door to another &lt;a href=\"Commoner%27s%20House%20%28Bridge%20District%29\"&gt;generic house&lt;/a&gt; and the front door faces the back of the &lt;a href=\"Five%20Flagons%20Inn\"&gt;Five Flagons Inn&lt;/a&gt;. The front door is unlocked. The interior consists of only one room that's loaded with boxes, bags, crates, and four hostile individuals.\nMod content.\nInstallation of the &lt;a href=\"Golem%20Construction%20for%20Spellcasters\"&gt;Golem Construction for Spellcasters&lt;/a&gt; Mod adds a &lt;a href=\"Stone%20Golem\"&gt;Stone Golem&lt;/a&gt; to the creatures within, presumably belonging to Dracondros. \nInstallation of the &lt;a href=\"Sword%20Coast%20Stratagems\"&gt;Sword Coast Stratagems&lt;/a&gt; Mod makes some changes to the building's inhabitants. See the individual creature pages for a summary of revisions."}
{"id": "48677", "revid": "35642161", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=48677", "title": "Storehouse (Docks District)", "text": "This Storehouse is located in the &lt;a href=\"Athkatla%20Docks\"&gt;Docks District&lt;/a&gt; next to the &lt;a href=\"Shadow%20Thief%20Guildhall\"&gt;Shadow Thief Guildhall&lt;/a&gt;. The front door is unlocked. It's devoid of people between 5:30 am and 5:30 pm. During the evening hours a quartet of randomly spawned individuals may appear. The locked chest is the only locked container of the four.\nMod content.\nThe \"&lt;a href=\"Tactics%20Mod\"&gt;Tactics Mod&lt;/a&gt;\" component \"Lich in the Docks\" places a powerful female lich and her allies inside this house, who attack the party on sight.\nThe \"&lt;a href=\"Fade%20NPC\"&gt;Fade NPC&lt;/a&gt;\" mod causes the quest character Xek'ral (Fade's brother) to spawn here at a specific point during one of Fade's personal quests in &lt;a href=\"Baldur%27s%20Gate%20II%20Chapter%206\"&gt;chapter 6&lt;/a&gt;.\nThe \"&lt;a href=\"Back%20to%20Brynnlaw\"&gt;Back to Brynnlaw&lt;/a&gt;\" mod has a key meeting in this Storehouse to kickstart the adventure in &lt;a href=\"Baldur%27s%20Gate%20II%20Chapter%206\"&gt;chapter 6&lt;/a&gt;. Note that the installation of either of the mods above needs to be resolved first, or the key creature will be present with the Lich in the Docks. Which is not ideal."}
