{"id": "46967", "revid": "265273", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=46967", "title": "Storm Shield", "text": "Storm Shield is a &lt;a href=\"special%20ability\"&gt;special ability&lt;/a&gt; of the &lt;a href=\"Cleric\"&gt;Cleric&lt;/a&gt; kit &lt;a href=\"Priest%20of%20Talos\"&gt;Priest of Talos&lt;/a&gt;. It sets to 100% the caster's resistances to &lt;a href=\"Electricity%20damage\"&gt;Electricity&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Fire%20damage\"&gt;Fire&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Cold%20damage\"&gt;Cold&lt;/a&gt; damage, and makes them immune to &lt;a href=\"Protection%20From%20Normal%20Missiles%23Affected%20items\"&gt;these projectiles&lt;/a&gt;. From level 1 to 9, all effects last 1 turn. From level 10, they last 1 round per level of the caster, up to 20 rounds at level 20 and above."}
{"id": "8321", "revid": "47673695", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=8321", "title": "Storm Star", "text": "Storm Star +3 is an enchanted mace which inflicts 1d6 +4 points of crushing damage and 1d6 points of electrical damage. The weapon has -3 THAC0\u00a0bonus, a speed factor of 4 and it weighs 6 lbs. This item appears in and .\nThis item can be acquired by pressing a certain combination of buttons and levers in the &lt;a href=\"Machine%20of%20Lum%20the%20Mad\"&gt;Machine of Lum the Mad&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Watcher%27s%20Keep\"&gt;Watcher's Keep&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;a href=\"Cespenar\"&gt;Cespenar&lt;/a&gt; can upgrade this mace for some gold and the &lt;a href=\"Starfall%20Ore\"&gt;Starfall Ore&lt;/a&gt;.\nUpgraded.\nStorm Star +5 inflicts 1d6 +6 points of crushing damage and 1d6 points of electrical damage. Also, there is a 5% chance a successful hit may cause a &lt;a href=\"Chain%20Lightning\"&gt;Chain Lightning&lt;/a&gt;. The mace also gives the wielder 20% resistance to electrical damage. The weapon has a -5 THAC0 bonus, a speed factor of 2 and it weighs 4 lbs."}
