{"id": "4257", "revid": "47673695", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=4257", "title": "Violet Potion", "text": "Violet Potions raise the &lt;a href=\"strength\"&gt;strength&lt;/a&gt; of the consumer to 25 for a full 24 hours. However, during this, the &lt;a href=\"constitution\"&gt;constitution&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"dexterity\"&gt;dexterity&lt;/a&gt; of the user are lowered to 3. It can be consumed by all classes except Wizard Slayer. This item appears in &lt;a href=\"Baldur%27s%20Gate%20%28game%29\"&gt;Baldur's Gate&lt;/a&gt; and . This potion can be bought from a merchant in one tent at the &lt;a href=\"Carnival\"&gt;Carnival&lt;/a&gt;. The player has one chance to buy one potion for . The same merchant also sells the &lt;a href=\"Red%20Potion\"&gt;Red Potion&lt;/a&gt;.\nUsage.\nThis potion can be consumed without being identified.\nIt is one of the few items allowing certain classes to open both containers containing the tomes in &lt;a href=\"Candlekeep%20Catacombs\"&gt;Candlekeep Catacombs&lt;/a&gt; on a solo run, since they either require &lt;a href=\"Knock\"&gt;Knock&lt;/a&gt;, a relatively high &lt;a href=\"Thief\"&gt;Open Locks&lt;/a&gt; skill, or a &lt;a href=\"Strength\"&gt;Strength&lt;/a&gt; score above 22 to bash open. Most notably this includes Clerics, Druids, Shamans and Abjurers. Fighter type classes could also use a &lt;a href=\"Potion%20of%20Cloud%20Giant%20Strength\"&gt;Potion of Cloud Giant Strength&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=\"Potion%20of%20Storm%20Giant%20Strength\"&gt;of Storm Giant Strength&lt;/a&gt;."}
